---
---
<section id="research" class="section container scroll-trigger">
    <div class="research-header">
        <div class="swiss-badge" style="display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 24px;">Case Studies & Science</div>
        <h2 class="display-lg">The science is settled.</h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Case Study 1: Forgetting Curve -->
    <div class="article-card">
        <div class="grid-2">
            <div>
                <div class="swiss-badge" style="margin-bottom: 24px; display: inline-block;">Study 01 / The Problem</div>
                <h3 class="display-md">The Illusion of Competence.</h3>
                <p class="body-md study-text">Rereading notes feels productive, but it is an illusion. Your brain recognizes the words and tricks you into thinking you've learned them. But recognition is not recall.</p>
                <p class="body-md">In 1885, Hermann Ebbinghaus discovered the <strong>Forgetting Curve</strong>. Within 24 hours of passive reading, the human brain forgets up to 70% of new information. Without intervention, knowledge decays exponentially.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="graph-box">
                <div class="graph-title">The Ebbinghaus Forgetting Curve</div>
                <svg viewBox="0 0 400 250" width="100%">
                    <line x1="40" y1="200" x2="380" y2="200" stroke="#e5e7eb" stroke-width="2" />
                    <line x1="40" y1="20" x2="40" y2="200" stroke="#e5e7eb" stroke-width="2" />
                    <text x="5" y="30" font-family="Inter" font-size="12" fill="#6b7280">100%</text>
                    <text x="5" y="195" font-family="Inter" font-size="12" fill="#6b7280">0%</text>
                    <path class="draw-path anim-draw" d="M 40,20 Q 80,180 380,190" fill="none" stroke="#ef4444" stroke-width="3" stroke-dasharray="5,5" />
                    <path class="draw-path anim-draw-delay-1" d="M 40,20 Q 60,100 100,120 L 100,20 Q 150,60 200,90 L 200,20 Q 280,30 380,40" fill="none" stroke="#10b981" stroke-width="4" />
                    <circle cx="100" cy="120" r="4" fill="#10b981" class="fade-up-element anim-fade-in" />
                    <circle cx="200" cy="90" r="4" fill="#10b981" class="fade-up-element anim-fade-in-delay" />
                </svg>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Case Study 2: Karpicke 2008 -->
    <div class="article-card scroll-trigger">
        <div class="swiss-badge" style="margin-bottom: 24px; display: inline-block;">Study 02 / The Antidote</div>
        <h3 class="display-md">Karpicke & Roediger (2008):<br>The 200% Retention Increase.</h3>
        
        <div class="grid-2 study-grid">
            <div>
                <p class="body-md study-text">In a landmark study published in the journal <em>Science</em>, researchers Karpicke and Roediger tested students on Swahili-English vocabulary pairs.</p>
                <ul class="study-list body-md">
                    <li><strong>Group 1 (Passive Study):</strong> Repeatedly restudied the material but were not tested.</li>
                    <li><strong>Group 2 (Active Recall):</strong> Were repeatedly tested on the material (forced retrieval) without studying it again.</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="article-quote">"Testing is not just a way to assess learning; it is one of the most powerful ways to cause learning."</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="graph-box">
                <div class="graph-title">Final Retention (1 Week Later)</div>
                <svg viewBox="0 0 300 200" width="100%">
                    <line x1="0" y1="160" x2="300" y2="160" stroke="#e5e7eb" stroke-width="2" />
                    <g class="bar-group-1">
                        <rect x="50" y="100" width="60" height="60" fill="#ef4444" rx="4" />
                    </g>
                    <text x="80" y="90" font-family="Inter" font-size="16" font-weight="600" fill="#ef4444" text-anchor="middle" opacity="0" class="fade-up-element anim-fade-in-delay">33%</text>
                    <text x="80" y="180" font-family="Inter" font-size="12" fill="#6b7280" text-anchor="middle">Passive</text>
                    <g class="bar-group-2">
                        <rect x="180" y="30" width="60" height="130" fill="#10b981" rx="4" />
                    </g>
                    <text x="210" y="20" font-family="Inter" font-size="24" font-weight="600" fill="#10b981" text-anchor="middle" opacity="0" class="fade-up-element anim-fade-in-delay">80%</text>
                    <text x="210" y="180" font-family="Inter" font-size="12" fill="#6b7280" text-anchor="middle">Active Recall</text>
                </svg>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .research-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    .study-label {
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        font-size: 11px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--ink);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .study-text { margin-bottom: 16px; }

    .study-grid {
        align-items: start;
        margin-top: 32px;
    }

    .study-list {
        padding-left: 20px;
        color: var(--body);
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .study-list li { margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .study-list li:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

    .article-quote { font-size: 16px; margin: 24px 0; }

    .graph-box {
        background: var(--surface-soft);
        padding: 24px 16px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .graph-title {
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--ink);
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .bar-group-1,
    .bar-group-2 {
        transform: scaleY(0);
        transform-origin: bottom;
    }
    .bar-group-1 { transform-origin: 80px 160px; }
    .bar-group-2 { transform-origin: 210px 160px; }
    .is-visible .bar-group-1 { animation: growUp 1s ease-out forwards; }
    .is-visible .bar-group-2 { animation: growUp 1s ease-out 0.4s forwards; }
    @keyframes growUp { to { transform: scaleY(1); } }
</style>
